{"tid":167870,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"同事俾人叫左去走貨，可以點做？","createTime":"2017-03-23T06:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T08:20:31.000Z","uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ffcb785f722cd2c2ad7f71fa6a2ac7f18add0069","tid":167870,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T06:46:35.000Z","msg":"是咁的，個同事一直都做得嘢<br />\n不過呢排經濟真係好差<br />\n咁大家都知做sales要跑數嫁啦<br />\n咁經濟差，我地為左要令其中一個人跑到數就谷落其中一個同事度(跑唔到出最低工資)<br />\n一個到數好過全部都唔到數<br />\n咁跟住我地間鋪嘅員工就被拆散，我俾人調走左(已辭職)<br />\n另外一個同事就經常要走貨<br />\n其實呢啲程況可以點做？係咪應該反面？<br />\n求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0c98e6e2f84493dfc3f93d14d2d3b9c819829c","tid":167870,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T06:51:18.000Z","msg":"今次真係認真post"},{"pid":"80794258f2f93b843ccb48471079d9b9673424b5","tid":167870,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T06:53:15.000Z","msg":"咩叫走貨先"},{"pid":"b4acced2fb2a2548d4a8465d94e66dc533334b9f","tid":167870,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T06:53:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩叫走貨先</blockquote><br />\n將啲貨運去唔同鋪"},{"pid":"41e5a5c9a0672a1904ce604ed77dfb2f138c7027","tid":167870,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T06:58:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩叫走貨先</blockquote><br />\n將啲貨運去唔同鋪</blockquote><br />\n但平時冇呢個人"},{"pid":"55f4e6a5807e2e448edcd37f179f92fd77880060","tid":167870,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:04:44.000Z","msg":"走啦都冇計....一你叫佢同上便講"},{"pid":"0c16fbe0bfa5181d5fe9c527724eebcc05705c4a","tid":167870,"uid":62289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:06:55.000Z","msg":"直係唔比個同事 跑數<br />\n叫佢做 其他野？"},{"pid":"de0ba912cebfd6e9a16f61feaa41ab6f